            }
          ],
          "level_range": null,
          "section": "Leveling Rotation for Protection Warrior Tank in Burning Crusade",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=25264",
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "text": ": Thunder Clap reduces incoming damage by ~17% and must always be applied on the boss."
        },
        {
          "entities": [
            {
              "id": 30022,
              "name": "Devastate",
              "type": "spell",
              "url": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=30022"
            }
          ],
          "level_range": null,
          "section": "Leveling Rotation for Protection Warrior Tank in Burning Crusade",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=30022",
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "text": ": Use Devastate with spare rage whenever your other abilities are on cooldown."
        },
        {
          "entities": [
            {
              "id": 2565,
              "name": "Shield Block",
              "type": "spell",
              "url": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=2565/shield-block"
            }
          ],
          "level_range": null,
          "section": "Leveling Rotation for Protection Warrior Tank in Burning Crusade",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=2565/shield-block",
              "text": "Shield Block"
            }
          ],
          "text": "Shield Block : Use Shield Block to force proc Revenge or for damage mitigation if you have spare rage."
        },
        {
          "entities": [
            {
              "id": 78,
              "name": "Heroic Strike",
              "type": "spell",
              "url": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=78"
            }
          ],
          "level_range": null,
          "section": "Leveling Rotation for Protection Warrior Tank in Burning Crusade",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=78",
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "text": ": Finally, only use HS if you have spare rage, without ever going overboard and risking delaying your main abilities."
        },
        {
          "entities": [
            {
              "id": 25264,
              "name": "Thunder Clap",
              "type": "spell",
              "url": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=25264"
            }
          ],
          "level_range": null,
          "section": "Leveling Rotation for Protection Warrior Tank in Burning Crusade",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=25264",
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "text": ": Thunder Clap is your strongest ability to generate equal threat on up to 4 targets and should be used on cooldown if 2 targets or more."
        },
        {
          "entities": [
            {
              "id": 25203,
              "name": "Demoralizing Shout",
              "type": "spell",
              "url": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=25203"
            }
          ],
          "level_range": null,
          "section": "Leveling Rotation for Protection Warrior Tank in Burning Crusade",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=25203",
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "text": ": Demo Shout greatly reduces incoming damage against large groups, but is weak for threat generation below a dozen targets."
        },
        {
          "entities": [
            {
              "id": 30356,
              "name": "Shield Slam",
              "type": "spell",
              "url": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=30356"
            }
          ],
          "level_range": null,
          "section": "Leveling Rotation for Protection Warrior Tank in Burning Crusade",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=30356",
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "text": ": Shield Slam remains your best single-target threat ability, to use on cooldown."
        },
        {
          "entities": [
            {
              "id": 25264,
              "name": "Thunder Clap",
              "type": "spell",
              "url": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=25264"
            }
          ],
          "level_range": null,
          "section": "Leveling Rotation for Protection Warrior Tank in Burning Crusade",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=25264",
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "text": ": Thunder Clap should be used on cooldown for AoE."
        },
        {
          "entities": [
            {
              "id": 30022,
              "name": "Devastate",
              "type": "spell",
              "url": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=30022"
            }
          ],
          "level_range": null,
          "section": "Leveling Rotation for Protection Warrior Tank in Burning Crusade",
          "source_links": [
            {
              "href": "https://www.wowhead.com/tbc/spell=30022",
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "text": ": Use Devastate as your main filler, if rage allows for it."
